This paper is about natural language processing and specifically discourse parsing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to improve performance, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions the use of back-translations, which is a technique commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural machine translation (cs.NE).
